## 3. Redistribution
Redistribution of the base of PopulaireCoreGL **prohibited** without prior written consent from **OpenDeskTeam**. \
If you modify the program, you can redistribute your modified version under the following conditions:
- You must provide **clear attribution** to **OpenDeskTeam** as the original author.
- You must include a copy of this license with any redistributed version.
- You must state that your version is a **modified version** and not the original.
- You may not use the name "OpenDeskTeam" or any of its trademarks without prior written permission.
- Be comptatible with other OS using PopulaireCoreGL as a base.
